original: Lindeberg, Karl Edvard, distrikts-lantmätare, Jönköping, f. 26/11/85 i Nikolai, Södermani. 1., av Edvard L. o. Amalia Krogh. G. 16 m. Dagny Johansson. Barn: Maj f. 18, Inga 20, fil. kand., Karl-Göran 23, banktj :man. — Mog:ex. 07, lantmät:ex. 12. Distr:-lantmät. 23, i Jönköp. distr. sed. 34. RVO.
translated: Lindeberg, Karl Edvard, district surveyor, Jönköping, b. 26/11/1885 in Nikolai, Södermanland, 1st son of Edvard L. and Amalia Krogh. Married on 16th with Dagny Johansson. Children: Maj b. 1918, Inga b. 1920, Bachelor of Arts, Karl-Göran b. 1923, bank clerk. Completed magistrate examination in 1907 and surveyor examination in 1912. District surveyor since 1923, in Jönköping district since 1934. Order of the Royal Vasa (RVO).
